title: Ubuntu 12.04.4 LTS 32 and 64 bit Editions
description:
UBUNTU 12.04.4 LTS 32 AND 64 BIT EDITIONS

     This long term support edition of Ubuntu is supported until April 2017. I notice it takes a while with direct download to get the .iso so if we get a torrent going with plenty seeders, it will be faster download even if you have a 1.5-3 meg dsl connection, the servers there at ubuntu can get tied up at times, us seeders here at the pirate bay sharing with fast connections can help, I have a 7-8meg adsl download rate at the time I think my upload rate is 3 megs I will start this out when I sleep at maxing the up rate at 150 kbps, then when someone gets 1 seed ratio they can seed and the speed for others can go up depending how fast they share.
